commit.message:
feat(misc): i18n, cli vanity;

- Error labels for PortalUpdater.
- New messages.

feat(misc): comments;

- Added inline comment for tests.
- Fixed return of abort in new view.

feat(cli): activity deletion;

- Improved activity deletion capabilities.
- Updated template copy and translations.

